sec.p:
Recordings were retrieved between June 2019 and April 2021. In total 63 patients (39 male) were included, from which 6 had two or three periods of follow-up because of re-hospitalisation. This resulted in 70 recording periods described in Table 1. Twenty-nine recordings include at least one exacerbation, with 36 total exacerbations.
